flightsim.simconnect
Interface Dispatcher

All Known Implementing Classes:
AbstractDispatcher, DispatcherTask
public interface Dispatcher

Base interface for dispatchers. Dispatchers handle a buffer containing raw data as received from the network. It has to be parsed and to generate a valid RecvPacket subclass. AbstractDispatcher is one of them.
